creator: E.Mall solutions
descriptionHtml:
1. When you add your favorite product to favorites, you will receive your own offers. (By pressing the heart symbol next to the product).
2 - shop at your convenience from your favorite mall and at the same prices.
3 - Save time and effort searching for offers.
4 – saving companies offers for a longer period.
5 - Honesty in dealing and commitment to prices.


Seller's Guide:
You can easily display your commercial goods. And identify the strengths and weaknesses of your product through customer ratings and feedback.
You ‘’as a seller’’ are requested to:
1 – take care of products image as it reflects the value of the product and the shop.
2- To get a commercial status registered with the Syrian State, so that there is credibility in the work.
3 - The offer of goods allowed to be sold and declared by the Syrian authority.
4 - take care of prices to be competitive in the market.
descriptionShort: The first e-market in Syria, which provides comfort, saving & entertainment.

title: Magic Mall

creator: E.Mall solutions
descriptionHtml:
Magical is an application and shopping site that contains the first electronic supermarket with a home delivery service in Damascus and the new Levant.
We strive to provide everything that matters to the home and family, delivered to the door with the push of a button. Do not delay requesting any product or service from the Customer Care Department.
We offer you the luxury of shopping via a mobile device from home with ease and security, with reasonable prices, more options and high quality with a guarantee of payment after receipt.
We specialize in dealing with groceries, vegetables, fruits, meat, cheese, dairy and juice products. The platform contains a marketplace for stores belonging to the most important companies.
We also provide meals and sacrifice services, and the ability to carry out party requests.

Magical Corporate Services.


Magical is an e-commerce platform since the beginning of 2019, including the first electronic supermarket in Syria.

Magical provides companies with unique promotional and logistical services that help the marketing department to study this promising market and targeted promotion within it with the help of data and information provided to you by specialists within Magical. electronic space.

As the first electronic supermarket in Syria, Magical has distinguished customers who chose to embrace the culture of e-shopping at an early stage, and to go to this innovative segment with professional tools with an important marketing dimension for those who foresee the future and the growth it holds for e-shopping globally and changing the purchasing habits of consumers and its impact on changing retail supply chains.
descriptionShort: An e-commerce platform that includes the first electronic supermarket in Syria
